{"tid":2501670,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"［月經］有冇貼3M隔熱嘅巴打會貼埋天窗？","createTime":"2021-04-23T14:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T14:42:45.000Z","uid":63371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6039ad255010339893de46c0bdd95d68ebdb86db","tid":2501670,"uid":63371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T14:13:07.000Z","msg":"唔係tesla嗰種全透明，係有天幕/天窗簾，有冇需要貼埋？<br />\n因為3M官網嗰幾間特約施工商都唔同價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一間$1500<br />\n一間$800<br />\n一間$500<br />\n但全車就一樣$6800<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打幫襯過 auto beauty/autoever 呢2間特約施工商？<br />\n<br />\n名車就睇巴打講（不過係鍍膜）話明星幫襯就好好服務，街客就hea 鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以有啲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"552caf8f118951039b07a78b6ea4b437295136ed","tid":2501670,"uid":13416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T14:36:34.000Z","msg":"我幾年前autobeauty貼<br />\n貼完幾日有隻窗仲有好多氣泡<br />\n番去叫佢再做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191b3e48921d013816152e8ac4f71109a34a4301","tid":2501670,"uid":84013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T14:42:45.000Z","msg":"1）睇你有冇需要<br />\n2）睇你錢多唔多"}]}